TITLE: URL Generation Examples in UserController
DESCRIPTION: Multiple examples showing different ways to generate URLs using RouterInterface, including query parameters and fragments.
SOURCE: https://github.com/spiral/docs/blob/3.14/docs/en/http/routing.md#2025-04-20_snippet_52

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
use Spiral\Router\RouterInterface;

// ...

public function index(RouterInterface $router)
{
    $uri = $router->uri('home', ['action' => 'index']);

    dump((string)$uri); // /home/index

    $uri = $router->uri('home', [
        'action' => 'index',
        'page'   => 123
    ]);

    dump((string)$uri); // /home/index?page=123

    $uri = $router->uri('home', [
        'action' => 'index',
        'page'   => 123
    ]);

    dump((string)$uri->withFragment('hello')); // /home/index?page=123#hello

    $uri = $router->uri('home', [
        'action' => 'hello World',
    ]);

    dump((string)$uri); // /home/hello-world
}
```

