TITLE: Configuring Complex Role Permissions with Rules in Spiral
DESCRIPTION: Advanced configuration of role permissions using wildcard patterns and custom rules in a Spiral Bootloader.
SOURCE: https://github.com/spiral/docs/blob/3.14/docs/en/security/rbac.md#2025-04-20_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
