TITLE: Defining Message Entity with Cycle ORM Annotations in PHP
DESCRIPTION: This class represents a message entity in the chat application using Cycle ORM annotations. It defines relationships to Thread and User entities and implements JsonSerializable for API responses.
SOURCE: https://github.com/spiral/docs/blob/3.14/docs/zh-CN/cookbook/simple-chat.md#2025-04-20_snippet_0

