TITLE: Using WeakReference Binding with String Alias
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to use WeakReference binding with a string alias in the container.
SOURCE: https://github.com/spiral/docs/blob/3.14/docs/zh-CN/container/configuration.md#2025-04-20_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
use Spiral\Core\Container;
use WeakReference;

public function boot(Container $container): void
{
    $object = new stdClass();
    $hash = \spl_object_hash($object);
    $reference = WeakReference::create($object);

    $container->bind('test-alias', $reference);

    dump($hash === \spl_object_hash($container->get('test-alias'))); // true

    unset($object);
    // 
    dump($container->get('test-alias')); // null
}
```

