TITLE: Defining Message Entity in Spiral ORM
DESCRIPTION: This code defines the Message entity using Cycle ORM annotations. It includes relationships to Thread and User entities, and implements JsonSerializable.
SOURCE: https://github.com/spiral/docs/blob/3.14/docs/en/cookbook/simple-chat.md#2025-04-20_snippet_15

LANGUAGE: php
