TITLE: RoadRunner Configuration for Centrifugo Integration
DESCRIPTION: This YAML snippet configures RoadRunner to communicate with Centrifugo. It defines the RPC listener, server command, and Centrifuge-specific settings like proxy and GRPC API addresses.
SOURCE: https://github.com/spiral/docs/blob/3.14/docs/zh-CN/websockets/configuration.md#2025-04-20_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: yaml
CODE:
```
```yaml .rr.yaml
rpc:
  listen: tcp://0.0.0.0:6001

server:
  command: "php app.php"
  relay: pipes

centrifuge:
  proxy_address: "tcp://0.0.0.0:10001"
  grpc_api_address: "centrifugo:10000"
```
```

